TASK: Given a text file Find the count of all Words in each sentence using any one of the Data Structures

FGEN.PY:
        This is a Interactive Python Script for generating the Text File.
        Words in the file are generated by appending random Alphabets to a word according to user intended Word Length(range).
        Sentence in the file are generated by appending the Words randomly created, User can specify Min and Max number of words in a Sentence.
       
WORDCOUNTER.JAVA:      
        This is a interactive Java Program for counting the words in each line of the text file.
        User is required to provide filename along with complete file path (eg:$ pwd\*.txt)
